9aee815\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n<li>Highly flexible and energy efficient home heating systems. It works by extracting heat from the outside air, raising this heat to a higher temperature and then distributing warmth around your home.<\/li>\n<li>Altherma technology gives you 3 to 5 times the efficiency of traditional boiler systems. In other words, for every \u00a31 you put in, you get back 3 to 5 pounds worth of heat.<\/li>\n<li>Altherma can provide all your heating and hot water all year round.<\/li>\n<li>Altherma is compatible with radiators, fan coils and underfloor heating.<\/li>\n<li>A heat pump system consists of an outdoor unit, and indoor hydrobox, and a domestic hot water tank.<\/li>\n<li>VAT on domestic heat pump installations is only 5%<\/li>\n<li>Daikin Altherma is accredited under the Microgeneration Certification Scheme, allowing homeowners to apply for grant of up to \u00a35000 under the Low Carbon Building Programme.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li>Carbon emissions are reduced by up to 50%, with energy savings of up to 30%.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fa130f4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"fa130f4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Key Benefits<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7b23821 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7b23821\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li>30-50% reduction in CO2 emissions.<\/li><li>Low running costs.<\/li><li>Low maintenance.<\/li><li>Low Noise &#8211; Unobtrusive and quiet.<\/li><li>Easy to install &#8211; No Groundwork or digging.<\/li><li>No gas supply, flues or ventilation required.<\/li><li>No fuel storage tanks required.<\/li><li>Suitable for both houses and apartments.<\/li><li>Single phase power supply, low starting current.<\/li><li>Weather compensation built in as standard.<\/li><li>Meets and exceeds CO2 reduction targets required by building regulations.<\/li><li>Helps achieve 3 star rating in the code for sustainable homes<\/li><li>Reduced VAT for domestic applications from 20% to 5%.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9913187 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9913187\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0f074f2 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"0f074f2\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c2230aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c2230aa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Talk to us<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-14b235b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"14b235b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Have any questions? We are always open to talk about your business, new projects, creative opportunities and how we can help you.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4f55473 elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-butt